# Copy to .env and adjust as needed. Vite only exposes VITE_-prefixed vars, and
# bakes them in at BUILD time (so on Netlify this must be set before `vite build`).

# Optional override for the API base URL. Leave UNSET in both dev and production:
# the app then uses relative "/api/..." requests (same origin) — proxied to the
# local backend by the Vite dev server (vite.config.ts) in dev, and served by the
# Netlify Function in prod. Only set this to point the SPA at a remote/absolute API.
# VITE_API_URL=
